jobInfo.postDescription:
You will join the overseas digital development team of ZEEKR, responsible for overseas system requirement review, technical architecture design, coding, and other work, and work closely with the European team and domestic team to deliver requirements on time and with quality. The specific work includes, but is not limited to, the following:

● Collaborating with the product manager to review requirements, design architecture, code, test, and other related work for ZEEKR's overseas digital products.
● Being responsible for ensuring the stability of the system online, and promptly discovering and solving online problems.

You will report to the CN Bigdata Technical Team Leader.

Job Requirements:

● Fluent spoken English is essential. Candidates with overseas project experience will be given priority consideration.
● Bachelor's degree or above in software engineering or a computer-related field.
● Solid foundation in Java, familiar with basic libraries, understanding of Java polymorphism, multithreading, IO, and so on.
● In-depth understanding of mainstream open-source frameworks such as Spring, MyBatis, and familiar with big data components
● Have a certain level of technical solution design ability and can independently complete the product's research and development and delivery.
● Passionate about technology, with a preference for candidates who have experience writing blogs and contributing to open-source projects.
● Good at communication and teamwork, able to proactively drive problem-solving.

brandComInfo.introduce: 浙江极氪智能科技有限公司于2021年3月成立，同年4月发布极氪品牌及首款产品——豪华猎装轿跑ZEEKR 001。 作为一家以智能化、数字化、数据驱动的智慧出行科技公司，极氪由吉利汽车、吉利控股集团（含员工跟投平台和用户权益平台）共同投资成立。秉承平等、多元、可持续的价值观，极氪智能科技聚焦智能电动出行前瞻技术的研发，以科技共创潮流生活，为用户创造极致体验。
